	<p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><i><b>The Bachelor Party</b></i> is a 1953 teleplay by <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paddy_Chayefsky" title="Paddy Chayefsky">Paddy Chayefsky</a> which was adapted by Chayefsky for a 1957 film.</p>
	<h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Television">Television</span></h2>
	<p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Chayefsky's teleplay was produced by <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Coe" title="Fred Coe">Fred Coe</a> for <i><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Philco_Television_Playhouse" title="The Philco Television Playhouse">The Philco Television Playhouse</a></i> on October 11, 1953. <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Delbert_Mann" title="Delbert Mann">Delbert Mann</a> directed the following cast:</p>
